# 3. 大きな差

Haruka: *Nod* I think that was the best run we've had of it so far.
Airi: Yeah! Then, let's take a ten-minute break, but let's not forget how that felt!
Minori: Okay! Time for some water...
Minori: Oh, Shizuku, that reminds me! Have you heard back about your audition yet?
Shizuku: Oh...
Shizuku: No, I haven't heard back from them... It's been almost a week, so I think it should be soon...
Airi: Well, it's best not to dwell on this stuff! You know what they say! Good things come to those who wait.
Saito: Shizuku! The results of that audition just came in!
Shizuku: ...!
Haruka: Right on cue.
Minori: S-So, how did she do...?!
KAITO: Really...?! It's wonderful to hear that you passed.
Rin: Congratulations, Shizuku!
Shizuku: Yes, thank you.
Minori: And you're gonna be working with Hagiyama from ReLight, right?! She seems like the perfect choice, since she has such a nice shine to her! Now I can't wait to see your commercial!
Haruka: Me neither. There's no doubt that she's good, so I'm sure you two are going to produce a great commercial.
Shizuku: Yes, well...
Airi: Wait, you don't seem all that happy for some reason. Is something wrong?
Shizuku: The truth is... I'm scared.
Haruka: You're scared...?
Shizuku: I'm afraid that I'm going to ruin this commercial.
Minori: What?!
Airi: Ruin it? What makes you think that?
Shizuku: Because Hagiyama was truly overwhelming during that audition...
Shizuku: I took one look at her and realized that she possesses something which I don't.
Shizuku: I'm honestly wondering if I have what it takes to be paired with her...
Airi: Slow down...! What do you mean you don't have what it takes? That's ridiculous—
Shizuku: That's just the truth of it. She stands miles ahead of me.
Rin: But...
Miku: In other words, this Hagiyama girl must really be something else.
Shizuku: She is...
Shizuku: However, if I keep feeling this way, it's definitely going to negatively affect the quality of our commercial.
Shizuku: They chose me, so I need to do my best to make it as good as I possibly can.
Minori: Shizuku...
Haruka: Okay... But you shouldn't have to carry this all on your own.
Airi: What she said. We're here to help, so ask us if you ever need any!
Miku: We should be able to give you some assistance by watching you pose and such...!
Shizuku: All of you...
Shizuku: Thank you. I really appreciate it.
Shizuku: (We start shooting in just a few weeks. I honestly don't know how much I'll be able to improve by then.)
Shizuku: (But if it means getting even a little bit closer to the brilliance Hagiyama possesses...)
Shizuku: (I have to try...! For the sake of MORE MORE JUMP!)
